:59 PM ET cutoff, A1010/26 had been replaced by A1015/26, which preserved a western-Tehran-FIR closure but listed more exceptions and different operative text. This bears on scope, exact operative source, and whether plaintiff's A1010 reports are sufficient without the actual current NOTAM text.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T16:01:30Z\",\"sha256\":\"f736eb543e7c927519c42f6c43f328b9646ec2d9d2783a4b3e9b9e05cbd9be0e\",\"size_bytes\":1657,\"source_description\":\"Captured text from Notamify page for FIR OIIX NOTAM A1015/26. The page presents raw NOTAM text, issue/effective timestamps, and states it replaces OIIX A1010/26.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/67435351-52f9-4d17-8f4c-497a21dd94bf\",\"storage_name\":\"f7/f736eb543e7c927519c42f6c43f328b9646ec2d9d2783a4b3e9b9e05cbd9be0e\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify raw NOTAM OIIX A1015/26 replacing A1010/26\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T15:48:36Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_f994792e9085_unresolved-record-gaps\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"unresolved-record-gaps.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"f994792e9085a3bd6c36ca810b27151f53b6c7209b170c3493b715f197f39bef\",\"size_bytes\":911,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"f9/f994792e9085a3bd6c36ca810b27151f53b6c7209b170c3493b715f197f39bef\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"unresolved-record-gaps.txt\"}]},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T16:21:20.280378088Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C1\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":886079,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":9}}"}],"details":{"mode":"call","mcpResult":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nm